{"tid":2289094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大和田]捷克外交部：支那破壞一國兩制賦予香港的自治、政治多元及自由","createTime":"2020-11-17T04:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T01:57:36.000Z","uid":51271,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5184b3141f0182ad9edc518309755e0c1fae12d7","tid":2289094,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T04:22:02.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20201117/mobile/bkn-20201117091213793-1117_00952_001.html</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n捷克外交部當地周一（16日）就多名香港泛民立法會議員被取消議員資格發聲明，指北京當局的決定打擊香港的一國兩制。中國駐捷克大使館發言人回應稱，捷克外交部粗暴干涉香港事務和中國內政，表示強烈不滿和堅決反對。<br />\n捷克外交部的聲明指，北京此舉破壞一國兩制賦予香港的自治、政治多元及自由，捷克會持續在歐盟會議上支持及維護香港的自治。"},{"pid":"92a3ae9af72bc53203a3768f492667b8230ec8a8","tid":2289094,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T04:25:13.000Z","msg":"可以準備mail merge定捷克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aea13eddece901c2ae7166efb0a1a16fa9a842c","tid":2289094,"uid":384679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T04:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/CapitalEachDanishswedishfarmdog-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FCapitalEachDanishswedishfarmdog-size_restricted.gif&h=a7c8b65a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ca00c75f4c37675d0d7603a0c7a35eefd066a9a","tid":2289094,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T04:33:40.000Z","msg":"捷克咁pro支都反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f279fca3933170d4f1b2bedaca23dca0bf1cc9b7","tid":2289094,"uid":45523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6ca00c75f4c37675d0d7603a0c7a35eefd066a9a","tid":2289094,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T04:33:40.000Z","msg":"捷克咁pro支都反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20